{"tid":334975,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[好玩唔玩玩屎]不滿被捕　男子拉屎吃下再吐到警察身上","createTime":"2017-07-25T08:16:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T01:14:10.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"eec728c0a11735f0662c25dce7891a063a62198e","tid":334975,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T08:16:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170725/640_b92df457fc78482aa4b888ca74f3dd73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170725%2F640_b92df457fc78482aa4b888ca74f3dd73.jpg&h=a71f28ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國舊金山東灣里奇蒙（Richmond）一名奇男子為了要表達被捕時的不滿，<span style=\"color: red;\">在警車上開始脫衣服、排泄，甚至還「趁新鮮」開吃，並吐到警員身上</span>，不過就算如此他最後還是逃不了被關的命運。<br />\n<br />\n根據當地電視台KRON 4報導，17日晚間兩名警員獲報前往逮捕一名男子，該名男子為了躲避被捕，先是謊報了一個假名字，好巧不巧這個假名也在拘捕名單上，於是他報上真名，還是在拘捕名單上，男子認了只好束手就擒。<br />\n<br />\n當一行人回到警局後，警方發現他其實在保釋期間，男子開始不願意配合登記列案，警員因此要將他移送監獄，途中男子上了手銬，<span style=\"color: red;\">但他開始脫衣服，再把衣服丟出窗外，並且大肆解放，警方回頭查看到底發生什麼事時，被他吐了滿臉大便。</span>最後警方不得不臨停，公路巡警前來支援，暫時封閉道路，並確認雙方安全後，男子還是被送進監獄了。（陳其仙／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170725/1168246/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170725%2F1168246%2F&d=73CgSGyxYnNN2c6jUkTuj5UJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=6152f651\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170725/1168246/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mt4PF7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMt4PF7.jpg&h=b5717ebb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73f41beab7d4f50637982102c65dd383c50e23db","tid":334975,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T08:17:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hk